query:
/*+ NoHashJoin(t1 s1) NoMergeJoin(q1 s1 t1 tq1 u1) NoNestLoop(account q1 q2 s1 t1 tq1 tq2 u1 u2 t2) NoNestLoop(account q1 q2 s1 t1 t2 tq1 tq2 u1 u2 s2) */ select account.display_name
from tag AS t1
inner join site AS s1
on t1.site_id = s1.site_id AND t1.name = 'machine-learning' AND s1.site_name = 'stats'
inner join tag_question AS tq1
on tq1.tag_id = t1.id AND tq1.site_id = s1.site_id
inner join question AS q1
on tq1.question_id = q1.id AND q1.site_id = s1.site_id
inner join so_user AS u1
on q1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND q1.site_id = u1.site_id
inner join so_user AS u2
on u1.account_id = u2.account_id
inner join account AS account
on account.id = u1.account_id
inner join question AS q2
on q2.owner_user_id = u2.id AND q2.site_id = u2.site_id
inner join tag_question AS tq2
on tq2.question_id = q2.id
inner join tag AS t2
on tq2.tag_id = t2.id AND t2.name = 'button'
inner join site AS s2
on tq2.site_id = s2.site_id AND t2.site_id = s2.site_id AND q2.site_id = s2.site_id AND s2.site_name = 'stackoverflow';
